  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A multicenter Prospective Study to assess the screening methods, parameter of NTX and the
      efficacy and safety of zoledronic acid treatment in addition to anti-tumor therapy in
      patients of non-small cell cancer with bone metastasis in china.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
